findings.title: Owner can change router address
findings.description: The owner has privileges to change the router address.

findings.title: Owner can change marketing and charity addresses
findings.description: The owner has privileges to modify marketing and charity addresses without restrictions.

findings.title: Owner can change max transaction amount
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to modify the maximum transaction amount.

findings.title: Owner can change and restore fees
findings.description: The owner has privileges to modify and restore fees, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can exclude addresses from fees
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude certain addresses from fees.
